description:
English translation of the Japanese manga Strike Witches - Tenkou no Otometachi (ストライクウィッチーズ天空の乙女たち).

Strike Witches is the highly popular 'dieselpunk' franchise that spans manga, light novels, video games and anime. The series reimagines World War II as a confrontation between the allied human forces and an invading alien menace. In 1939, an enigmatic alien force called the Neuroi launched a widescale invasion of Earth, destroying nation after nation. Humanity's last hope at survival is to form an international elite fighting force of flying aces known as the Strike Witches! These young women possess innate magical powers and have been equipped with the latest in military technology: Striker Units, which provide the user with a unique array of weaponry that can only be controlled by magic. Enter a young healer named Yoshika Miyafuji, the newest inductee into the 501st Joint Fighter Wing. Yoshika may be opposed to the military, but if she wants to survive, she better learn quick from veteran ace and strict disciplinarian, Mio Sakamoto, just exactly what it means to be a Strike Witch!
name: Strike Witches: Maidens In the Sky

description: Perfect Nonsense tells the story of one of the most innovative and under-rated Golden Age artists, children's illustrator and nonsense poets in American history. For more than 50 years, George Carlson created distinctive cartoons, comics, riddles, and games that thrilled both children and adults with their fanciful spirit and nonsensical humor. Until now there had never been a career retrospective of this startling creator and this book will astonish cartoon and comics aficionados, teachers of children's media, scholars of American humor, and anyone interested in the ever-evolving landscapes of image and language.
name: Perfect Nonsense: The Chaotic Comics and Goofy Games of George Carlson

deck: The story of an ordinary student, Nagasumi Michishio, and his unforgettable summer experience involving mermaids, mafia members, and forced marriage that will turn his life upside-down.
description:
Seto no Hanayome which literally mean "The Inland Sea Bride" (English Title: My Bride is a Mermaid), revolves around Nagasumi Michishio and Sun Seto.

The story starts Nagasumi went into a family vacation with the purpose of visiting his grandmother. He went swimming at a nearby beach and suddenly experience leg cramps, he thought himself dead when a visage of a what seems to be a mermaid rescued him then he passed-out. He woke at the voice of his father waking him up and he told him what happened. Of course Nagasumi's father did not believe him.

Later, at night time, a mysterious girl showed up and told Nagasumi to marry her.
name: Seto no Hanayome

description:
Digital chapters for the Amnesia graphic novel.

One of the most feared terror attack scenarios involves the detonation of a weapon that generates a powerful electromagnetic pulse (EMP) that immediately renders power circuits, computers, even automobiles useless. But what if a weapon was discharged that, in addition to all the above, also erased people's memories? Would mankind, given a fresh start, continue on its path to self-destruction? Or would it, free of its preconceptions, usher in a new age of peace? Amnesia explores what might happen if someone were to push the restart button on the human race.
name: Amnesia

description:
Digital chapters for the second Fafnir the Dragon graphic novel.

The irreverent, violent, and satirical Fafnir is back! This time, the dragon travels through time and no one is safe. Meet Barack, Rush, and many others as they interact with Fafnir in the past, present, and future. If he screws things up, it's just the end of civilization as we know it. No pressure... Buckle up!
name: Fafnir the Dragon

description:
Digital chapters for The Hope Virus graphic novel.

Herbert is a social outcast at school and deals with his gloomy boredom through his website www.thehopevirus.com. After struggling with fitting in at school and his unusual case of insomnia, Herbert falls into a deep coma. He awakens to realize that his blogs have become some of the most quoted and influential scriptures of history. _x000B_Helen, a young girl under rule of The Hope Virus Holdings (HVH), reveals to Herbert that his thoughts and journaling have lead to the worst oppression the world has even seen. Herbert now realizes that he must break the very world he created.
name: The Hope Virus
